    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS. This unit is paired with a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from recent subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings to maintain optimal suspension geometry. The engine pulls linearly to its 8,000 RPM redline, showing excellent compression across all cylinders. While displaying minor aesthetic wear consistent with its mileage, its performance remains uncompromised, offering a pure analog driving experience with sharp throttle response and communicative steering rack feedback.",
