      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between daily utility and premium comfort. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only the minor road wear expected of a well-loved car, such as a few faint stone chips on the front bumper. Inside, the cabin is a pristine, non-smoker environment; the leather upholstery has been regularly conditioned to maintain its suppleness, and every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in its prime. It has followed a rigorous service schedule with full synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles, and the transmission shifts with seamless precision. We recently installed a fresh set of tires and performed a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure total peace of mind. There are no leaks, no warning lights, and no hidden stories\u2014just a smooth, quiet, and dependable ride that reflects years of careful ownership. This is an honest, well-sorted machine ready for its next long-term home.",
      "price": 36800.0,
